quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,46,"Ini: \"ar yiwet kan, ara kwen nabi$: a pbeddem zdat Öebbi, di sin, ne$ weêêedwen; sinna, a d tesmektim. Ameddakwel nnwen ur illi d aôehbani. Neppa d aneddaô nnwen kan, uqbel aâaqeb uqsiê"
  34,47,"Ini: \"ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiât; apan nnwen. Ih, taqdiât iw, ar Öebbi kan. Neppa, $ef yal cci, d Anagi"
  34,48,"Ini: \"ih, Mass iw Ipqeddim tidep, d Amusnaw n tbavnit"
  34,49,"Ini: \"tusa d tidep, ur d nezzunt tkerkas, ur d ppalsent"
  34,50,"Ini: \"ma nnetlafe$, nnetlafe$ kan i iman iw. Ma pwanha$, d ayen iyi d Iweêêa Mass iw. Neppa, ih, d Aqôib, Isell"
  34,51,"Lemmer a pwaliv mi xelâan, tarewla ur telli. Pwaîîfen, si tama iqeôben"
  34,52,"Nnan: \"numen yis\". Amek ara d ssiwven, si tama ibaâden"
  34,53,"Ni$ llan zik, nekôen t. Rran akin tabavnit, si tama ibaâden"
  34,54,"Ad yili ufûil, garasen d wayen ctaqen, akken tevôa, zik, d wid i ten icban. Ih, nitni llan di ccekk imcebbwel"